onomous artificial intelligence agent developed by Peter Steinberger. It is an autonomous agent that can execute tasks via large language models, using messaging platforms as its main user interface. OpenClaw achieved popularity in late-January 2026, credited to its open source nature and the viral popularity of the Moltbook project. On February 14, 2026, Steinberger announced he will be joining OpenAI and the project will be moved to an open-source foundation.\",\"AbstractURL\":\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OpenClaw\",\"Answer\":\"\",\"AnswerType\":\"\",\"Definition\":\"\",\"DefinitionSource\":\"\",\"DefinitionURL\":\"\",\"Entity\":\"software\",\"Heading\":\"OpenClaw\",\"Image\":\"/i/0bd2b6dcfe4cc34e.png\",\"ImageHeight\":270,\"ImageIsLogo\":1,\"ImageWidth\":1316,\"Infobox\":{\"content\":[{\"data_type\":\"string\",\"label\":\"Developer(s)\",\"value\":\"Peter Steinberger\",\"wiki_order\":0},{\"data_type\":\"string\",\"label\":\"Written in\",\"value\":\"TypeScript, Swift\",\"wiki_order\":1},{\"data_type\":\"string\",\"label\":\"Operating system\",\"value\":\"Cross-platform\",\"wiki_order\":2},{\"data_type\":\"string\",\"label\":\"Type\",\"value\":\"AI agent, Autonomous agent, Autonomous personal, assistant\",\"wiki_order\":3},{\"data_type\":\"string\",\"label\":\"License\",\"value\":\"MIT License\",\"wiki_order\":4},{\"data_type\":\"twitter_profile\",\"label\":\"Twitter profile\",\"value\":\"openclaw\",\"wiki_order\":\"102\"},{\"data_type\":\"instance\",\"label\":\"Instance of\",\"value\":{\"entity-type\":\"item\",\"id\":\"Q7397\",\"numeric-id\":7397},\"wiki_order\":\"207\"},{\"data_type\":\"instance_2\",\"label\":\"Instance of\",\"value\":{\"entity-type\":\"item\",\"id\":\"Q3467906\",\"numeric-id\":3467906},\"wiki_order\":\"207\"},{\"data_type\":\"instance_3\",\"label\":\"Instance of\",\"value\":{\"entity-type\":\"item\",\"id\":\"Q4826847\",\"numeric-id\":4826847},\"wiki_order\":\"207\"},{\"data_type\":\"instance_4\",\"label\":\"Instance of\",\"value\":{\"entity-t